"""
src/config.py
=============
Central configuration — Single Source of Truth for the EduInfra Ghana pipeline.

All file paths, column names, scoring weights, design constants, and the
high-fidelity Ghana national boundary geometry live here so every other
module imports from a single, authoritative location.
"""

